      <div class="msgContentFrame">Good news and bad news from yesterday... <br /> <br />The bad new is, I was trying to get marks, and didn't get a single one... <br /> <br />The good new is that I got a super uber leve draw yesterday with 4 lvl 20 and 2 lvl 25 leve on the same day, spread in only 2 cities (didnt even bother to visit the third one). <br />It seems most people around my leve had a good draw (and pretty similar requierments) too in my LS. I wonder if anybody noticed that. <br />I also wonder if it is consitent between various serveur. <br /> <br />For me <br />Serveur: Figaro <br />GLD lvl 21 at start (and 21 at finish anyway) <br />leve optained (from memory) <br />Limsa: <br />- lvl 20 can't remember, maybe brass rings <br />- lvl 20 blue bandana <br />- lvl 20 green bandana <br /> <br />Ul'thla <br />- lvl 20 brass rings <br />- lvl 25 silver circlet (thunder stone) <br />- lvl 25 silver circlet (wind stone) <br /> <br />Anybody from around my lvl got that kind of draw yesterday?  <br /> <br />Still 0/6 on mark is a pain, I'm about 1/20 now since I have been high enough to do lvl 20 ones (and I don't get more than 1 or 2 lvl 20 leve/day, sometimes 0...).  <br />Either I'm uber unlucky or if is again a balance issue where you just get mark once in a blue moon if lucky... It's like the 1/24 miner ones i'm on, still can't buy the ability I want after 3weeks of lvl 20 leve, even having done the lvl 20 quest. It is getting better since I turned 25 and get 4/day instead of too, 3/32, if I don't fail today, I should get my ability tonigh...  <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 19th 2010 10:42pm by Anurid </span></i></div>
