      <div class="msgContentFrame">Each of the local leve has a variant of level, it might be 1,5,15,25,40 etc. and it's totally random each leve reset which level will be available for that leve. Ul'dah has the highest number of Goldsmith local leves available, doesn't meant it will guarantee high level leve, as I've said this is totally random. The only thing you can do is check all three cities. <br /> <br />I've gained 5170 Guild Marks in about 45+ Goldsmith leves past rank 20. The rank 20 will give 400 GMs with evaluation under 100, rank 30 seems to give 700 GMs with evaluation under 100. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 21st 2010  3:59am by Khornette </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1807831.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /></div></div>
